# TestPage/Tables

Unfortunately, Markdown has a *very* limited table syntax. The first row must be a header, and you cannot use col-spacing or row-spacing or different alignment in different cells.

| Cell1 | Cell2 |
|-------|-------|
| Cell3 | Cell4 |

## Different cell sizes

